    {
        "url": "/quotes/vivek_wadhwa_614559",
        "quote": "My message to students is that if you want to become an entrepreneur and save the world, definitely don't skip college. But go to a school that you can afford. You'll be freed from the chains of debt and succeed on your own ambition and merit.",
